data.description: This is an amazing home featuring 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 baths and is an open concept floor plan, great for being connected with the family.Jackson Heights a developing subdivision in a great location. It features high ceilings allowing you to feel liberated, granite counter tops with plenty of counter space and the outdoor covered porch is great for activities, BBQs and gatherings! The master bedroom is something to talk about and that closet, WOW! It is large enough to consider a room unto itself. This premier design with an island and built-ins may even provoke your wife to allow you access for your clothes, too! This home won't last long!
